cac:ProcurementProject.cbc:Name: UCDOPP5287 Grounds Maintenance and Sports Pitches (including Artificial Surfaces) Maintenance to University College Dublin
cac:ProcurementProject.cbc:Description: University College Dublin is seeking to establish a sustainable Multi Supplier Framework Agreement for the provision of Grounds Maintenance and Sports Pitches including Artificial Surfaces Maintenance to University College Dublin. There are six Lots as follows Lot 1. Grounds Maintenance, Lot 2. Sports Pitch and Artificial Surfaces Maintenance, Lot 3. Road Maintenance including Gritting, Snow Ploughing, Road Sweeping and Road Drainage Maintenance, Lot 4. Tree Surgery, Lot 5. Grounds Maintenance Projects and Lot 6. Supply of Trees, Plants and Landscaping Products.

efac:SelectionCriteria.cbc:Description: As detailed in the procurement documents

cac:FrameworkAgreement.cbc:Justification: The investment in equipment required by the contractor to deliver the required services as the main site location has landscaping in over two hundred and eighty acres with a variety of requirements.
